summoning-machine-phase-blade-name = Nanoluminite phase blade
summoning-machine-phase-blade-desc = A heavy pre-Fracture blade with switchable combat tuning. It looks exactly as unhealthy to argue with as it should.
summoning-machine-magboots-name = Pre-fracture magboots
summoning-machine-magboots-desc = Advanced combat magboots for people who consider deck plating, hull plating, and open space equally valid footing.
summoning-machine-kasatura-combat-name = Kasatura combat exosuit (removable, 120 seconds)
summoning-machine-kasatura-combat-desc = A rare pre-Fracture exosuit that binds to its wearer. It can be removed, but not by anyone in a hurry.
summoning-machine-kasatura-centurion-name = Centurion kasatura (removable, 120 seconds)
summoning-machine-kasatura-centurion-desc = A reinforced Kasatura for anyone who thinks normal armor sounds more like a suggestion.
summoning-machine-kasatura-prefect-name = Prefect kasatura (removable, 120 seconds)
summoning-machine-kasatura-prefect-desc = A command-grade Kasatura for senior field officers who prefer their armor to make the chain of command obvious.
summoning-machine-autopulser-name = Kunis system autopulser
summoning-machine-autopulser-desc = A pre-Fracture plasma rifle where the word "auto" matters a lot more than the word "discussion".
summoning-machine-combat-jumpsuit-name = Combat jumpsuit
summoning-machine-combat-jumpsuit-desc = A base layer for people planning to fight first and explain themselves later.
summoning-machine-combat-gloves-name = Combat gloves
summoning-machine-combat-gloves-desc = Fireproof, impact-ready, and noticeably better than bare hands when sparks or faces are involved.
summoning-machine-double-emergency-oxygen-tank-name = Double emergency oxygen tank (filled)
summoning-machine-double-emergency-oxygen-tank-desc = A compact double oxygen reserve. Small, full, and usually important one moment before it becomes critical.
summoning-machine-jetpack-name = Pre-fracture jetpack (filled)
summoning-machine-jetpack-desc = An exotic pre-Fracture jetpack with a full tank. A strong counterargument to gravity.
summoning-machine-jaws-of-life-name = Jaws of life
summoning-machine-jaws-of-life-desc = A scientific-magical rebuttal to doors, plating, and anyone overly confident in hull integrity.
summoning-machine-power-drill-name = Power drill
summoning-machine-power-drill-desc = A simple powered hand drill. Fast, loud, and perfect for the moment a screwdriver stops being persuasive.
summoning-machine-combat-medkit-name = Combat medkit
summoning-machine-combat-medkit-desc = For situations where "we'll get you to medbay later" has already stopped sounding credible.
summoning-machine-compact-defibrillator-name = Compact defibrillator
summoning-machine-compact-defibrillator-desc = A pocket-sized way to restore discipline to a heart. It can also settle rougher discussions.
summoning-machine-antique-battery-name = Antique battery prototype
summoning-machine-antique-battery-desc = A self-recharging relic from old weapons programs. Tiny, strange, and suspiciously useful.
summoning-machine-antique-battery-emp-proof-name = EMP-proof antique battery prototype
summoning-machine-antique-battery-emp-proof-desc = The same ancient battery, now with attitude and EMP shielding. Rare enough to make people possessive.
summoning-machine-mass-scanner-name = Handheld mass scanner [Borg]
summoning-machine-mass-scanner-desc = A borg-grade mass scanner for anyone who prefers exact numbers over optimistic guessing.
summoning-machine-cognizine-bottle-name = Cognizine bottle
summoning-machine-cognizine-bottle-desc = A bottle of cognizine. Sometimes the best way to expand your mind, sometimes the worst.
summoning-machine-syringe-name = Syringe
summoning-machine-syringe-desc = A plain syringe. Nothing fancy, except for how creatively it tends to get used.
summoning-machine-asakim-encryption-key-name = Asakim encryption key
summoning-machine-asakim-encryption-key-desc = An encryption key for the Asakim remnants channel.
summoning-machine-asakim-tracking-implanter-name = Asakim tracking implanter
summoning-machine-asakim-tracking-implanter-desc = A disposable implanter loaded with an Asakim tracking implant.
summoning-machine-rtg-flatpack-name = RTG flatpack
summoning-machine-rtg-flatpack-desc = A flat box with very non-flat power ambitions.
summoning-machine-asrg-flatpack-name = ASRG flatpack
summoning-machine-asrg-flatpack-desc = The moodier and more serious cousin of the RTG. Likes pressure, produces power.
summoning-machine-radiation-collector-flatpack-name = Radiation collector flatpack (filled)
summoning-machine-radiation-collector-flatpack-desc = A flatpack with a radiation collector and a full plasma tank. For people who prefer cooking power instead of hunting for it.
summoning-machine-asakim-srd-name = Pre-fracture SRD [AZAKIM BIOCODE]
summoning-machine-asakim-srd-desc = A resonant repair tool keyed to Asakim neural patterns. Happier fixing ships than holding conversations.
summoning-machine-asakim-ai-core-name = Pre-fracture faction AI core
summoning-machine-asakim-ai-core-desc = A screwable combat AI core configured for Asakim defence-force targeting parameters.
summoning-machine-chest-rig-name = Black tactical chest rig
summoning-machine-chest-rig-desc = A black chest rig for people who prefer to keep gear outside and problems inside.
summoning-machine-ert-backpack-name = ERT leader backpack
summoning-machine-ert-backpack-desc = Spacious enough for the plan, the backup plan, and a little extra confidence.
summoning-machine-mre-crate-name = MRE crate
summoning-machine-mre-crate-desc = A crate of old military rations. Not inspiring, but very effective at feeding a whole problem.
summoning-machine-beacon-wyrm-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Wyrm
summoning-machine-beacon-wyrm-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Wyrm. Cheap by beacon standards for a reason.
summoning-machine-beacon-omen-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Omen
summoning-machine-beacon-omen-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Omen. Light hull, fast response, disposable signal.
summoning-machine-beacon-asakim-small-name = Emergency beacon: small Asakim vessel
summoning-machine-beacon-asakim-small-desc = A single-use beacon for a small Asakim ship. More support than spectacle.
summoning-machine-beacon-nebula-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Nebula
summoning-machine-beacon-nebula-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Nebula. Modest cost, respectable output.
summoning-machine-beacon-zenith-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Zenith
summoning-machine-beacon-zenith-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Zenith. Baseline combat response, baseline price.
summoning-machine-beacon-crow-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Crow
summoning-machine-beacon-crow-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Crow. More expensive than the light hulls, still not top shelf.
summoning-machine-beacon-concord-x-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Concord X
summoning-machine-beacon-concord-x-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Concord X. Frigate-grade support starts to cost like it.
summoning-machine-beacon-zenith-a-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Zenith A
summoning-machine-beacon-zenith-a-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Zenith A. Frigate-grade response for commanders with a budget.
summoning-machine-beacon-zenith-e-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Zenith E
summoning-machine-beacon-zenith-e-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Zenith E. Rare, heavier, and priced accordingly.
summoning-machine-beacon-razor-n-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Razor-N
summoning-machine-beacon-razor-n-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Razor-N. Special hull, special bill.
summoning-machine-beacon-mantaray-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Mantaray
summoning-machine-beacon-mantaray-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Mantaray. Destroyer-grade intervention is never cheap.
summoning-machine-beacon-asakim-medium-name = Emergency beacon: medium Asakim vessel
summoning-machine-beacon-asakim-medium-desc = A single-use beacon for a medium Asakim ship. Expensive enough to imply intent.
summoning-machine-beacon-wyvern-name = Emergency beacon: ADS Wyvern
summoning-machine-beacon-wyvern-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the ADS Wyvern. Capital-grade arrival, capital-grade price.
summoning-machine-beacon-azimuth-name = Emergency beacon: Asakim Azimuth
summoning-machine-beacon-azimuth-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the Azimuth. Cruiser-grade privilege at cruiser-grade cost.
summoning-machine-beacon-stratostar-name = Emergency beacon: Asakim Stratostar
summoning-machine-beacon-stratostar-desc = A single-use beacon keyed to call the Stratostar. A heavy Asakim cruiser built for sustained sector operations.
